563
01:21:23,667 --> 01:21:24,667
Agh!

564
01:21:26,583 --> 01:21:27,667
Tell me now!

565
01:21:28,250 --> 01:21:30,042
What suspicions have ye confirmed?

566
01:21:30,125 --> 01:21:31,458
