628
01:25:52,458 --> 01:25:54,167
I had no choice.

629
01:25:58,833 --> 01:25:59,917
My Ffion.

630
01:26:01,375 --> 01:26:02,875
My daughter!

631
01:26:04,750 --> 01:26:05,750
