685
01:31:22,667 --> 01:31:23,875
I, a father...

686
01:31:26,208 --> 01:31:27,208
robbed of kin,

687
01:31:29,583 --> 01:31:30,708
even in this,

688
01:31:31,917 --> 01:31:34,708
a moment of unforgiving grief,

689
